	&lt;li data-end=&quot;733&quot; data-start=&quot;669&quot;&gt;The &lt;strong data-end=&quot;705&quot; data-start=&quot;676&quot;&gt;ICC Champions Trophy 2025&lt;/strong&gt; was hosted by &lt;strong data-end=&quot;732&quot; data-start=&quot;720&quot;&gt;Pakistan&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

